'''Mang Tomás''' ([[Tagalog language|Tagalog]] for "Mr. Tomás") is a [[condiment]] brand owned by [[Nutri-Asia, Inc.]] Its core product is a sauce similar to ''sársa'' (''[[lechon|lechón]]'' sauce) but made without ground liver. The product is sold in the [[Philippines]] as "Mang Tomas All-Around Sarsa" and as "Mang Tomas All-Purpose Sauce" in export markets. The product is named after Tomás "Mang Tomás" delos Reyes, a famous ''lechonero'' (purveyor of ''[[lechon|lechón]]'') from [[Quezon City#La Loma|La Loma, Quezon City]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pepper.ph/mang-tomas-getting-know-man-behind-sauce/|title=The History of Mang Tomas All-Around Sarsa|date=30 April 2014|publisher=|accessdate=28 October 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://dennisvillegas.blogspot.com/2009/05/mang-tomas-pioneer-philippine-lechonero.html|title=Mang Tomas: Pioneer Philippine Lechonero|publisher=|accessdate=28 October 2018}}</ref> 

